re-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19?lang=spa#p19\">Mateo 15:19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/heb/3.12?lang=spa#p12\">Heb. 3:12</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124235018\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/prov/29.23?lang=spa#p23\">Prov. 29:23</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/pride?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Orgullo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note5b\" data-full-marker=\"5b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124235021\" id=\"note5b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/walk-walk-with-god?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Andar, andar con Dios</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124235025\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/45.9?lang=spa#p9\">Isa. 45:9</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.30?lang=spa#p30\">DyC 58:30</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.32-33?lang=spa#p32\">Moisés 7:32–33</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note6b\" data-full-marker=\"6b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124235028\" id=\"note6b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/60.4?lang=spa#p4\">DyC 60:4</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124235032\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/40.15,17?lang=spa#p15\">Isa. 40:15, 17</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.19?lang=spa#p19\">Mos. 4:19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/m